Detailed Description

template<class DataType>
class DzTSortedArray< DataType >

A template class which embodies a sorted array style list.

This class is used to store items that do not require calling a copy constructor when copying objects from one memory space to another.

template<class DataType>
DzTSortedArray< DataType >::DzTSortedArray ( const DzTSortedArray< DataType > &  obj  ) 

Takes an unsorted array, copies it into this array and sorts it. For creating large arrays, it can be much faster to create an unsorted array, and then sort it, rather than sorting the items on insert.
